Package: PCORcpp
Type: Package
Title: Projection Correlation in C++
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Xie Zhongming
Maintainer: Xie Zhongming <xzm1@ruc.edu.cn>
Description: A C++ implementation of projection correlation between two random vectors using Rcpp and Armadillo. This package provides efficient computation of projection covariance, projection correlation, and independence testing.
License: GPL (>= 3)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Imports: Rcpp (>= 1.0.0)
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppArmadillo
SystemRequirements: C++11, OpenMP
